Pitch:

involve people:
- What is your most annoying problem? -> What steals time, money, discomforts you?
- We can help you
- helping you understand the problem better 
  - 5 Whys, proven management technique
- Others can help you
  - common solutions to that problem
  - design/build a product to help you
  - asking more questions, making everybody understand your problem better

